---
description: Small-phase workflow, progress, commits and milestone reviews
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

- Work on one numbered phase at a time.
- Select the next incomplete phase unless a dependency blocker requires prerequisite work.
- Run tests and make at most three meaningful repair attempts.
- Update `CURRENT_STATUS`, `TEST_LOG`, `CHANGELOG`, `KNOWN_ISSUES` and phase evidence.
- Commit after each successful small phase.
- Do not push after every phase; push only after an approved milestone.
- At milestones provide screenshots where supported and a click-by-click test checklist.
